 ('4', '4', 'en_us', 'Reformat', '2.0', '50.0', 'Magazine', NULL, '<p>A magazine being responsive beyond screens.</p>\n<p>The magazine format is challenged by exploring the unconquered space between analog and digital media, expressed as a flexible design that responds to the screen resolution – and to print. Through interviews with leading design studios, the content informed the design process. Reformat aims to change the existing mindset by proving that print can be one of many possible states of digital objects.</p>', '2011–2012', '2017-05-22 22:08:21', '2017-05-28 13:17:47', '200d1b35-2902-4670-8049-0cb2d7557586'),
 ('5', '5', 'en_us', NULL, '0.0', '0.0', NULL, '2011', NULL, NULL, '2017-05-23 21:43:40', '2017-05-23 21:47:51', '3ba4b369-c334-4a81-8df9-2bd3b6912093'),
